{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/offices-and-institutions/execution-sentence-imprisonment","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Execution of the sentence imprisonment","meta_description":"In a state of emergency visits to prisons, remand prisons, and security detention facilities are prohibited.\r\n","content":{"processed":"<p><strong>Rules and recommendations</strong></p>\n<p>In a state of emergency visits to prisons, remand prisons, and security detention facilities <strong>are prohibited</strong>. The ban is compensated by extending a possibility to have a call for 30 minutes per day. Also, prisoners are allowed to have a videocalls with their loved ones.</p>\n<p>Lawyers can go to prisons on behalf of clients. However, they <strong>must face masks</strong> in all of the areas of the facility, including dealings with the client. Lawyers can also communicate with clients online using the \"<strong><a href=\"https://www.cak.cz/scripts/detail.php?id=22485\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">Skype Defense</a></strong>\" program.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions/execution-sentence-imprisonment"},"valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":null,"situation_type":{"name":"Offices and institutions","path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"account_balance"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Helplines","path":{"alias":"/situations/stress-and-handling-impacts-pandemic/helplines","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_to":null},"situationArea":{"name":"Offices and institutions","path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"account_balance"},"situation":[{"id":"87b78b06-9783-503c-a962-ea8a3817748e","title":"Operation of Offices","path":{"alias":"/situations/o